---

<div class="w-full py-20 px-5">
  <div >
    <h5 class="text-3xl text-center font-semibold text-primary-500">
      Why Seed?
    </h5>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-center mt-2 mb-6 text-gray-600 px-4">
       With years of experience in the education industry, SEED Education brags about a team of counsellors dedicated to providing personalised guidance tailored to each studentsâ€™ ambition.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:gap-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-20">
    {
      whySeedData.map((wsd,index) => (
